title: Cafe Imbir - Ginger
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, International, Italian, Macrobiotic, Organic, Western, Take-out
description: Vegetarian restaurant with a spiritual theme. Menu denotes which options may be made vegan, plenty of vegan options. Also selling a small variety of health related products including but not limited to spices, oils, raw products. A large inventory of books available to browse or purchase covering a variety of topics from vegetarianism to psychology. Previously called Literary Cafe Ginger. Address in Russian: г. Киев, ул. Жилянская, 7.
